WEBVTT

01:38.680 --> 01:40.480
EPISODE 28

01:40.920 --> 01:42.480
What are your plans for later?

01:42.560 --> 01:44.840
I'm getting my intern pay
from Zhenyi Tech.

01:44.920 --> 01:46.440
Who's going with me?

01:47.440 --> 01:49.480
I made plans with Dazhong.

01:49.560 --> 01:52.240
It's... that time of the month for me.

01:52.320 --> 01:55.640
- You have no love.
- Even if I do, you won't get it.

01:55.720 --> 01:58.280
- I'm taking off. Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

01:59.560 --> 02:00.840
Weiwei?

02:00.920 --> 02:03.000
Fine, I'm free anyway.

02:04.080 --> 02:04.920
Let's go.

02:05.000 --> 02:08.080
Wait here. Nature calls. Be right back!

02:08.479 --> 02:09.600
Hurry!

02:10.120 --> 02:12.120
MEN'S ROOM

02:22.800 --> 02:23.960
Ms. Erxi?

02:24.400 --> 02:27.160
Didn't I say to pretend we're stranger?
Don't you understand?

02:27.240 --> 02:32.480
Wait, Ms. Stranger,

02:32.880 --> 02:35.200
you should look up, because...

03:20.880 --> 03:21.840
Bei Weiwei.

03:24.240 --> 03:26.080
I'm going to study abroad.

03:26.600 --> 03:28.800
I'm here to get my paperwork done.

03:29.960 --> 03:31.000
Congratulations.

03:32.440 --> 03:33.480
I...

03:37.000 --> 03:41.920
I'm sorry for causing
you and Xiao Nai trouble

03:42.360 --> 03:45.240
with my immature behavior.

03:47.600 --> 03:51.000
It's okay. Don't worry about it.

03:51.280 --> 03:52.120
Wei...

03:59.880 --> 04:02.160
Weiwei, I envy you,

04:02.680 --> 04:04.760
not just for your relationship
with Xiao Nai,

04:05.160 --> 04:09.280
but more for having such a sincere friend.

04:12.360 --> 04:14.880
Sincerity is the precious nature
of friendship.

04:15.600 --> 04:18.959
If you're sincere to others,
they will feel it,

04:19.920 --> 04:21.720
and treat you the same way.

04:22.200 --> 04:25.960
I'm sure you'll find invaluable friends.

04:27.720 --> 04:31.560
I understood that too late,
but I think I can still make amends.

04:32.240 --> 04:36.920
Thank you, Bei Weiwei.
I wish you all the best.

04:41.160 --> 04:42.000
What?

04:42.680 --> 04:44.600
- Best of luck to you.
- Okay.

04:45.920 --> 04:46.760
Bye-bye.

04:55.640 --> 04:59.120
What did the campus belle say, Weiwei?

04:59.360 --> 05:02.640
Somehow she looks prettier than usual.

05:03.480 --> 05:07.080
Nothing much. She said,
she's studying abroad next semester.

05:07.160 --> 05:10.720
And she's envious
that I have an awful best friend like you.

05:10.800 --> 05:13.840
Who are you calling awful?
We're BFFs, okay?

05:14.400 --> 05:15.880
Enough, already.

05:15.960 --> 05:19.640
Weiwei, once she's gone,
won't you be the campus belle?

05:21.360 --> 05:23.400
About that,

05:23.560 --> 05:25.920
write an anonymous post to the forum,

05:26.000 --> 05:28.320
- and say married women...
- What?

05:28.680 --> 05:32.760
No, girls with boyfriends
can't compete to be campus belle.

05:32.840 --> 05:35.760
- How's that?
- Just forget it.

05:35.840 --> 05:38.720
Married teenager,
you will be the campus belle.

05:44.720 --> 05:45.960
Go on in, I'll wait here.

05:46.040 --> 05:48.120
What? Come in with me.

05:48.200 --> 05:50.320
Wait in the lobby. No one will notice.

05:50.480 --> 05:51.760
I'll wait here.

05:52.080 --> 05:54.600
Let's go. It's fine.

06:00.000 --> 06:02.400
Sit here. I'll go get my money.

06:02.480 --> 06:03.840
If they dock my pay,

06:03.920 --> 06:06.080
you have to come up, when I call. Okay?

06:06.160 --> 06:07.160
Got it.

06:13.160 --> 06:15.160
ZHENYI MONTHLY

06:20.440 --> 06:23.560
Where have I seen this guy?

06:33.120 --> 06:34.880
He does work for Zhenyi!

06:37.240 --> 06:40.840
I got it.
Weiwei, here's your money back.

06:41.080 --> 06:43.040
Let's spend the rest on a feast!

06:43.120 --> 06:45.640
Heartless Xiaoling and Sisi
don't get to come.

06:46.480 --> 06:48.760
Do you know this guy?

06:50.040 --> 06:52.520
That's Mr. Li,
head of game development.

07:00.920 --> 07:03.360
- What's wrong?
- I'll tell you later.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.800
To ensure fairness,

07:08.880 --> 07:10.640
we must use the outside server

07:10.720 --> 07:14.080
provided by Fengteng,
with real gaming specifications.

07:14.440 --> 07:17.760
The rest is the same as our internal test.
Don't be nervous.

07:18.520 --> 07:20.400
I'm still nervous, Nai.

07:21.360 --> 07:24.200
Are you sure
I should go up with you first?

07:24.440 --> 07:27.840
You can't make me suffer this fate,
because I'm cute.

07:30.200 --> 07:33.360
No way! In terms of cuteness,
I'm definitely number one.

07:33.640 --> 07:37.840
Nai only wants you there as contrast,
to show off how pretty he is.

07:38.640 --> 07:41.160
Good, you're still joking around.

07:41.240 --> 07:42.760
That means you're not too nervous.

07:44.680 --> 07:46.240
We're a little nervous,

07:46.600 --> 07:50.080
but not as much as Ashuang,
who can't come due to nervous diarrhea.

07:50.760 --> 07:53.400
Ashuang flaked out
at this critical moment.

08:07.240 --> 08:09.840
Hello, the number you dialed
cannot be reached.

08:09.920 --> 08:12.120
- Sorry...
- Why is his phone off?

08:13.680 --> 08:15.000
Are you from Zhiyi?

08:15.080 --> 08:17.160
- Yes.
- Okay. Please follow me.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.760
Mr. Xiao?

08:24.080 --> 08:25.160
- Mr. Wang.
- Welcome.

08:25.240 --> 08:26.960
Mr. He, sorry to keep you waiting.

08:27.040 --> 08:28.880
No, we just got here, too.

08:28.960 --> 08:30.840
This is Zhiyi's team?

08:30.920 --> 08:33.520
Fresh college graduates.
Very young, indeed.

08:33.600 --> 08:34.440
That's right.

08:36.600 --> 08:38.159
- Mr. Li!
- Welcome!

08:38.240 --> 08:39.840
- Mr. Wang, Mr. He.
- Welcome.

08:39.919 --> 08:40.880
This is?

08:40.960 --> 08:43.080
Mr. Zhen's son is representing Zhenyi.

08:43.280 --> 08:44.920
This is Young Master Zhen.

08:45.840 --> 08:47.440
- Mr. Wang.
- Welcome.

08:47.760 --> 08:49.000
- Mr. He.
- Welcome.

08:49.760 --> 08:51.760
Every generation has its heroes.

08:52.200 --> 08:55.280
Seeing such young teams
makes me feel my age.

08:55.360 --> 08:58.160
Everyone's here. Let's move inside.

09:14.000 --> 09:17.000
- Why are their phones all turned off?
- What's wrong?

09:18.640 --> 09:19.600
Do you remember

09:19.680 --> 09:23.600
I said I saw someone I know,
when you had dinner with Meng Yiran?

09:23.680 --> 09:25.760
That guy works for Xiao Nai.

09:26.040 --> 09:29.760
I saw him with Mr. Li from Zhenyi Tech.

09:29.920 --> 09:33.080
What were they doing together?
Something's off.

09:33.280 --> 09:37.360
Erxi, do you think this spells trouble
for Xiao Nai?

09:38.240 --> 09:39.560
Not necessarily.

09:39.640 --> 09:42.400
Maybe they know each other
and met for a meal.

09:43.720 --> 09:45.240
It can't be that simple.

09:45.680 --> 09:47.280
I should call and ask.

09:49.840 --> 09:53.120
- The number you dialed cannot be...
- Still turned off?

09:53.200 --> 09:54.200
Don't fret, Weiwei.

09:54.280 --> 09:56.520
They must have turned off
their phones for the demo.

09:56.600 --> 09:58.040
That's why you can't get through.

09:58.560 --> 09:59.760
Let's go back.

10:10.400 --> 10:11.400
Mr. He.

10:13.320 --> 10:14.160
Mr. Wang.

10:16.520 --> 10:18.360
Since this is a private demo,

10:18.440 --> 10:21.480
just relax and be yourselves.

10:21.560 --> 10:24.400
We'll start
as soon as President Feng arrives.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.640
- Sure.
- Okay.

10:28.880 --> 10:29.920
President Feng is here.

10:33.240 --> 10:34.080
President Feng.

10:40.640 --> 10:41.560
Sit down.

10:43.960 --> 10:46.960
President Feng,
Zhiyi Tech's team is on this side.

10:47.040 --> 10:48.400
Zhenyi Tech's team is on that side.

10:48.480 --> 10:49.960
They will take turns

10:50.040 --> 10:51.480
and present their game demo.

10:54.080 --> 10:55.680
President Feng's flight is at one o'clock.

10:55.960 --> 10:57.600
Time is a bit tight.

10:57.880 --> 11:00.400
Each team will only have half an hour.

11:03.760 --> 11:05.240
Okay, let's get started.

11:06.240 --> 11:07.880
Mr. He and I decided

11:07.960 --> 11:10.800
Zhenyi will go first,
based on alphabetical order.

11:11.440 --> 11:13.280
Okay. Thanks, Mr. Wang.

11:19.960 --> 11:22.720
On behalf of Zhenyi Tech,

11:22.800 --> 11:25.360
I'm honored to present our game design.

11:26.120 --> 11:27.480
Right now,

11:27.560 --> 11:29.560
I may be the project director
for Zhenyi Tech,

11:30.040 --> 11:33.600
but even more so, I'm a seasoned
player of "A Chinese Ghost Story."

11:35.000 --> 11:37.840
All of Zhenyi's design
for "A New Chinese Ghost Story"

11:37.920 --> 11:42.040
consistently prioritizes players' needs.

11:43.280 --> 11:45.680
Players are drawn in by a game,

11:45.760 --> 11:49.000
not only for repeated fighting
and endless upgrading of levels.

11:49.080 --> 11:52.920
Human interaction and emotional attachment
are more important.

11:53.480 --> 11:55.800
So, on top of the basic gameplay,

11:55.880 --> 11:57.880
we've added more interactive functions,

11:58.200 --> 12:00.880
introducing more complex and interesting

12:00.960 --> 12:04.080
love system, family system,
camaraderie system,

12:04.160 --> 12:08.320
as well as hundred-men team quests.
Please watch our demo video.

12:24.160 --> 12:27.040
This concludes my presentation.
Thank you.

12:33.560 --> 12:34.440
Nice.

12:36.200 --> 12:37.600
Online gaming technology

12:37.680 --> 12:39.280
has reached a peak.

12:39.920 --> 12:41.120
Little breakthroughs

12:41.200 --> 12:43.480
can no longer generate
new excitement for players.

12:43.960 --> 12:47.120
I think Zhenyi has done a great job
with new gameplays.

12:47.560 --> 12:49.880
Yes, Zhenyi's work is interesting.

12:50.560 --> 12:53.160
Now, let's hear from Zhiyi's team.

13:23.800 --> 13:26.000
Hi, my name is Xiao Nai.

13:26.400 --> 13:29.240
My teammates and I will now present

13:29.320 --> 13:32.320
Zhiyi's design ideas

13:32.560 --> 13:34.720
for "A New Chinese Ghost Story."

13:44.000 --> 13:47.240
Your demo is so small.
Is this a rushed job?

13:47.760 --> 13:49.520
I hear you have very few programmers.

13:51.280 --> 13:52.120
Eight.

13:55.320 --> 13:56.800
You may all be top students,

13:57.240 --> 14:00.200
but that scale for R&D is a bit...

14:02.240 --> 14:04.000
Zhiyi may not have many programmers,

14:04.080 --> 14:07.040
but we're all well-rounded
and able to work independently.

14:07.800 --> 14:10.400
Our team members know one another well
and work in harmony.

14:11.040 --> 14:15.280
What's more, a small client
doesn't reduce the game quality.

14:15.360 --> 14:17.880
Instead, it's easier
for players to download.

14:18.000 --> 14:19.520
Hopefully in our demo,

14:19.600 --> 14:21.240
we can prove this to Mr. He.

14:22.320 --> 14:23.160
Let's start.

14:31.600 --> 14:32.840
Everything's set, Mr. Li.

14:35.080 --> 14:37.960
CONNECTING TO THE SERVER...

14:49.680 --> 14:50.880
NETWORK ERROR. SERVER IN MAINTENANCE.

15:24.240 --> 15:26.760
Fengteng provided us the same server.

15:26.920 --> 15:29.960
It worked for Zhenyi.
Why can't Zhiyi connect to it?

15:30.200 --> 15:31.880
Is it the game's problem?

15:32.640 --> 15:35.960
No, even the physical connection
is not usable...

15:38.280 --> 15:41.560
Physical connection? What's the matter?

15:42.120 --> 15:44.720
Is there something wrong with our server?

15:45.000 --> 15:46.360
What's going on?

15:47.200 --> 15:48.800
Check with the server room.

15:48.880 --> 15:49.920
Got it, Mr. Wang.

15:56.360 --> 15:58.480
Sirs, the head of the server room checked,

15:58.560 --> 16:00.960
and said our service configuration
for Zhiyi malfunctioned.

16:01.400 --> 16:03.400
For some unknown reason,

16:03.480 --> 16:05.560
the service configuration
shut off abnormally.

16:05.880 --> 16:08.720
It'll take half an hour to reboot.

16:09.040 --> 16:09.880
Half an hour?

16:10.200 --> 16:13.160
President Feng needs to go
to the airport in 45 minutes.

16:13.480 --> 16:15.480
President Feng's flight can't be delayed.

16:15.560 --> 16:17.440
Either make a decision now,
or move the demo.

16:17.520 --> 16:19.160
It's not realistic to move the demo.

16:19.440 --> 16:21.280
It depends on Mr. He's time.

16:21.360 --> 16:24.200
He'll be in the US for three months.
We can't wait.

16:24.760 --> 16:26.600
Why don't we make a decision now?

16:26.960 --> 16:30.440
I think Zhenyi's proposal is pretty good.

16:31.320 --> 16:33.160
Zhenyi's ideas are original.

16:33.240 --> 16:35.160
Zhiyi might not do as well.

16:35.240 --> 16:36.960
Auspiciousness is key in a partnership.

16:37.040 --> 16:40.200
- Zhiyi is unlucky from the get-go.
- Right.

16:40.280 --> 16:41.840
Connect to the mirror server.

16:43.680 --> 16:44.520
Mirror server?

16:52.560 --> 16:54.360
You have a backup server?

16:54.720 --> 16:56.560
You're using your own server?

16:56.840 --> 17:00.480
Your server's specs are different
from the one Fengteng provided.

17:00.560 --> 17:02.240
That's unfair to Zhenyi.

17:04.960 --> 17:06.160
Before the demo,

17:06.560 --> 17:09.920
we made backups on servers
with the same specifications,

17:10.480 --> 17:13.520
just in case anything went wrong.

17:16.680 --> 17:20.920
President Feng, this is the server's
access connection account.

17:22.040 --> 17:24.960
Fengteng's technicians can log in anytime,

17:25.040 --> 17:27.280
and check the server's system parameters.

17:30.320 --> 17:32.880
Online games are commercial products.

17:33.680 --> 17:37.600
Every second of the operation affects
the company's reputation and profit.

17:38.040 --> 17:40.200
That's why stability is imperative.

17:40.960 --> 17:44.040
Numerous internet disasters
have taken place in recent years.

17:44.280 --> 17:46.640
In order to avoid such a negative impact,

17:46.880 --> 17:49.480
Zhiyi considered
off-site disaster recovery,

17:49.560 --> 17:51.480
when we designed
our server infrastructure.

17:52.640 --> 17:55.720
Within this framework,
when a server is in trouble,

17:56.000 --> 17:59.960
a mirror server automatically kicks in,
allowing players to continue the game.

18:00.600 --> 18:03.600
Ensuring the game's normal operation

18:04.120 --> 18:06.600
and minimizing accidents

18:07.480 --> 18:09.760
have always been Zhiyi's goals.

18:10.040 --> 18:12.240
These are the promises
we make to Fengteng

18:13.720 --> 18:15.280
in our future partnership.

18:26.920 --> 18:28.280
I'm totally amazed

18:28.360 --> 18:32.080
that such a young team is so thoughtful
and prudent.

18:34.360 --> 18:35.680
Well-prepared.

18:37.400 --> 18:40.120
Mr. Wang, I don't believe in coincidences.

18:40.880 --> 18:42.840
Right, my men are looking into it.

18:44.440 --> 18:47.280
Now, my teammates will take turns
and present

18:47.480 --> 18:50.240
the gaming features
in "A New Chinese Ghost Story."

18:57.080 --> 18:59.120
We redesigned the engine,

18:59.200 --> 19:02.200
splitting the single-threaded logic
into multithread,

19:02.280 --> 19:06.320
maximizing the computing powers
of CPU and GPU.

19:10.680 --> 19:16.360
- President Feng, single thread means--
- I know what it means. Don't explain.

19:19.800 --> 19:22.480
The biggest difference between

19:22.560 --> 19:26.920
single-unit games and online games is
the interaction between players and NPCs.

19:27.480 --> 19:29.840
If the NPCs are rigid,

19:29.920 --> 19:31.680
players will miss out on a lot of fun.

19:32.480 --> 19:37.760
Therefore, we purposely created
an in-depth behavior tree for NPCs,

19:38.240 --> 19:40.600
making them more intelligent.

19:40.680 --> 19:44.360
So the interaction between NPCs
and players is livelier.

19:46.840 --> 19:47.680
Interesting.

19:48.840 --> 19:50.480
The weather pattern change in the game

19:50.560 --> 19:53.040
maximizes the simulation of reality.

19:53.280 --> 19:57.400
The seasons: spring, summer, fall, winter;
with the sun rising and the moon setting.

19:57.480 --> 20:00.680
There are beautiful sunny days,
as well as long spells of rain.

20:00.920 --> 20:03.680
Our objective is to allow
players to experience the fun of change,

20:03.760 --> 20:07.520
without ever leaving home. Thank you.

20:07.600 --> 20:09.480
Such complex scene changes

20:09.880 --> 20:12.120
require high-end computer hardware.

20:13.080 --> 20:15.800
If a computer upgrade is needed
to play the game,

20:16.400 --> 20:20.640
will that pose inconvenience
and added cost to our players?

20:22.560 --> 20:24.000
The answer to Mr. He's question

20:24.080 --> 20:25.760
is the key to our next presentation.

20:26.720 --> 20:28.840
Lowering the computer hardware requirement

20:28.920 --> 20:30.800
without sacrificing game quality

20:30.880 --> 20:33.640
has always been the goal
of our engine optimization.

20:33.720 --> 20:38.160
Now, we will demonstrate that with
a large-scale Hebo flood-fighting quest.

20:41.000 --> 20:42.600
- This is great!
- Yes.

21:05.480 --> 21:07.560
Since there are long spells
of rain in the game,

21:07.760 --> 21:09.640
floods are inevitable.

21:10.400 --> 21:14.560
Hebo flood is our cross-server
disaster relief quest.

21:14.960 --> 21:19.440
Aside from rescuing NPCs and sending them
to safety in a limited time,

21:19.840 --> 21:23.360
players also have to execute quests
like rebuilding and relief goods transfer.

21:23.560 --> 21:25.280
These quests form dynamic quest chains,

21:25.720 --> 21:29.880
to ensure players will not find
the quests tedious or tiresome.

21:30.680 --> 21:35.200
Now, we will simulate tens of thousands of
players simultaneously on the same quest,

21:35.640 --> 21:38.520
in a pressure test
of the server's performance.

22:04.360 --> 22:06.200
That's amazing!

22:06.480 --> 22:08.200
President Feng, I think...

22:09.000 --> 22:11.400
I know you understand. I won't explain.

22:11.480 --> 22:14.200
10,000 players are online at once,
and it runs so smoothly.

22:14.520 --> 22:15.760
It's incredible.

22:15.840 --> 22:17.440
Not just "A New Chinese Ghost Story,"

22:17.520 --> 22:19.880
if this technology applies to other games,

22:19.960 --> 22:21.800
our revenues will greatly...

22:32.000 --> 22:35.400
That concludes our design and ideas
for "A New Chinese Ghost Story."

22:36.560 --> 22:40.160
Finally, before I end the presentation,

22:40.560 --> 22:43.560
I'd like to share with you
Zhiyi Tech's mission statement.

22:44.320 --> 22:46.800
"Original work and cultural transmission."

22:49.200 --> 22:50.800
When we decided to start

22:51.360 --> 22:53.320
our own gaming company,

22:54.160 --> 22:55.960
many had doubts,

22:57.240 --> 22:59.560
because we are young and inexperienced.

23:00.360 --> 23:03.120
Also because many people still view gaming

23:03.880 --> 23:06.960
as wasting one's life away.
However, to me,

23:08.000 --> 23:12.000
a game is the same as a book, a movie,

23:12.480 --> 23:13.960
a museum.

23:14.680 --> 23:17.760
It isn't just entertainment.
It's also a medium.

23:18.240 --> 23:21.280
A medium bearing the duty
of cultural transmission

23:21.880 --> 23:25.280
is a means of showcasing culture
to the people.

23:25.360 --> 23:28.520
Even more so,
it is an imperceptible influence.

23:30.880 --> 23:32.920
While playing our game,

23:33.000 --> 23:34.800
players are fully immersed in it

23:34.880 --> 23:37.520
and able to experience
every refinement of Chinese culture.

23:38.000 --> 23:39.560
So, Zhiyi's objective

23:39.760 --> 23:42.440
isn't simply to create popular games.

23:43.400 --> 23:45.960
Through the world we create,

23:46.040 --> 23:48.640
we hope more people
will get to know Chinese culture.

23:49.200 --> 23:53.680
That's also why we have insisted on
researching and developing our own engine.

23:54.240 --> 23:59.000
Only our own engine can create
a unique world of Chinese civilization,

23:59.080 --> 24:01.000
completely different from other cultures.

24:01.760 --> 24:03.560
We want to create a world

24:03.920 --> 24:08.160
out of something that has remained
in text and imagination only.

24:08.240 --> 24:12.400
Of course, we won't force our ideas
and concepts onto players.

24:13.560 --> 24:17.840
Instead, these will be manifested and
embodied in the elements of our game.

24:18.600 --> 24:23.800
That is the mindset and aspiration
behind our game design.

24:27.280 --> 24:30.400
Fengteng also strives to promote
traditional culture.

24:31.280 --> 24:35.880
I'm glad to see
Zhiyi shares the same aspirations.

24:36.440 --> 24:37.520
Thanks, President Feng.

24:37.880 --> 24:41.400
That's our presentation. Thank you.

24:58.680 --> 25:01.200
Zhiyi's ideas are pretty good,

25:01.280 --> 25:04.760
but I personally believe
marketability is still a priority.

25:05.720 --> 25:07.600
Zhenyi Tech's interactive systems

25:07.680 --> 25:10.880
are better in terms of playability
and sustainability.

25:12.240 --> 25:14.120
I disagree with Mr. He.

25:14.200 --> 25:17.160
"A New Chinese Ghost Story" isn't
a simple extension of the old game.

25:17.480 --> 25:20.560
If the changes are subtle,
why bother launching a new product?

25:21.280 --> 25:24.480
Zhiyi Tech's game engine
is clearly more impressive.

25:24.840 --> 25:27.880
It can also be widely applied
across other games.

25:29.640 --> 25:32.720
- President Feng, it's about time.
- Okay.

25:34.360 --> 25:36.560
Thanks to both young teams,

25:36.640 --> 25:39.120
for presenting your proposals.

25:39.360 --> 25:42.880
Please wait and rest
outside the conference room.

25:43.200 --> 25:46.080
We'll discuss internally,
before announcing the result.

26:18.800 --> 26:21.760
Uncle Li, stop pacing. It's annoying.

26:23.200 --> 26:27.040
Things aren't looking up for us. I'm so...

26:27.120 --> 26:28.600
We've done all we can.

26:29.320 --> 26:31.200
I have given everything I've got.

26:31.640 --> 26:34.960
If I lose,
it means I'm simply less skilled.

26:38.440 --> 26:40.040
Did you arrange this beforehand?

26:40.120 --> 26:42.360
Why wasn't I clued in on the backup?

26:42.680 --> 26:43.720
Of course, you weren't.

26:44.200 --> 26:46.880
Before we came, Nai told me to be careful.

26:46.960 --> 26:49.040
I can't believe something did go wrong.

26:49.120 --> 26:51.840
I panicked and nearly forgot
about the backup.

26:52.840 --> 26:54.640
It's weird, though.

26:54.720 --> 26:58.080
Why would a perfectly fine server
suddenly malfunction?

27:10.240 --> 27:11.720
I'm flying to New York.

27:11.800 --> 27:14.000
Let's discuss the contract
when I come back.

27:15.000 --> 27:16.000
I'll be waiting.

27:19.080 --> 27:20.400
Thanks for coming.

27:20.920 --> 27:22.960
Your sincerity is duly noted.

27:24.120 --> 27:26.080
I hope to work with you in the future.

27:26.840 --> 27:27.680
Thanks, President Feng.

27:28.880 --> 27:30.800
Mr. He, walk me downstairs.

27:37.040 --> 27:38.120
Sorry about that.

27:52.400 --> 27:56.360
Although I hate to admit it,
you win this round.

27:56.440 --> 27:58.120
I'm convinced you outperformed me.

27:59.480 --> 28:00.400
Let's go.

28:12.400 --> 28:14.400
FENGTENG TECHNOLOGY

28:19.360 --> 28:21.120
Don't look so down.

28:21.440 --> 28:24.840
We may have lost,
but we need to show sportsmanship.

28:25.560 --> 28:29.360
In terms of technology and design,
we were utterly defeated by Zhiyi Tech.

28:30.120 --> 28:31.720
It's the truth.

28:33.040 --> 28:34.760
Don't feel dejected, though.

28:34.840 --> 28:38.520
We may have lost,
but we'll reflect on this experience,

28:38.600 --> 28:40.440
and be better prepared next time.

28:41.360 --> 28:44.920
We will create a better game
and beat Zhiyi Tech.

28:46.840 --> 28:49.400
Thanks for your hard work
in the past month.

28:49.480 --> 28:50.680
Go home and rest.

28:50.960 --> 28:51.920
- Sorry, Mr. Zhen.
- Sorry, Mr. Zhen.

28:54.080 --> 28:56.560
It's not your fault. Don't feel bad.

28:56.760 --> 28:59.320
I'm the project director.
Any blame is on me.

29:00.480 --> 29:02.640
If Fengteng hadn't moved up
the demo by 20 days,

29:03.200 --> 29:05.000
we could've done better.

29:06.120 --> 29:08.960
Take a three-day paid leave.
Recharge and return to work.

29:13.480 --> 29:14.320
Where's Mr. Li?

29:15.440 --> 29:16.720
Wasn't he behind us?

29:18.360 --> 29:20.320
Okay. I need to talk to him.

29:20.400 --> 29:21.480
Head back to the hotel.

29:21.560 --> 29:22.600
- Sure, Mr. Zhen.
- Sure, Mr. Zhen.

29:28.800 --> 29:34.320
Sorry, Mr. Zhen.
We didn't get the project.

29:35.280 --> 29:38.160
I was surprised, too.
I thought our plan was impeccable.

29:38.720 --> 29:40.880
I didn't know Xiao Nai was so clever

29:40.960 --> 29:43.040
and prepared a mirror server.

29:43.600 --> 29:47.120
Mr. He likely got found out.

29:48.440 --> 29:52.320
Okay, I know.
I'll console Young Master.

29:53.040 --> 29:55.800
All right. I should go, Mr. Zhen.

30:23.520 --> 30:25.560
I wonder how things went.

30:53.400 --> 30:54.520
You're back!

30:55.160 --> 30:56.920
I came to get you for late-night supper.

30:58.880 --> 31:02.000
- We won.
- That's fantastic!

31:05.640 --> 31:06.480
Cheers!

31:11.840 --> 31:14.240
Comrades, we got the project.

31:14.320 --> 31:16.160
We're amazing, aren't we? Huh?

31:16.240 --> 31:17.600
- Yes.
- That's for sure!

31:17.680 --> 31:20.440
It was easy as one, two, three.
No question.

31:24.160 --> 31:26.160
Thanks for all of your hard work.

31:26.240 --> 31:28.560
Thank you, I drink to you guys.

31:28.640 --> 31:29.760
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

31:29.840 --> 31:31.200
- Drink!
- Drink!

31:36.400 --> 31:38.440
I thought you'd be celebrating
in Shanghai.

31:38.640 --> 31:39.760
Why did you come back?

31:40.400 --> 31:43.320
Because we miss you guys!

31:43.400 --> 31:46.840
We still have to discuss the contract.
Let's celebrate in Shanghai next time.

31:46.920 --> 31:48.040
- Right.
- Okay!

31:48.120 --> 31:51.320
Eat up, everyone.
Someone's picking up the tab.

31:52.320 --> 31:54.320
No one's leaving here sober!

31:54.400 --> 31:55.640
For sure.

31:55.720 --> 31:58.160
I've been waiting for this feast.

31:58.240 --> 32:00.840
I didn't touch the airplane food.
I'm starving!

32:02.560 --> 32:06.160
Order more dishes.
We can't let Nai off that easy tonight.

32:07.160 --> 32:08.360
We still have so much food.

32:08.880 --> 32:10.280
Are you silly or what?

32:10.360 --> 32:12.520
It's a rare opportunity
to get a feast out of Nai.

32:12.840 --> 32:15.720
Plus, I'm a key player on the team.

32:16.120 --> 32:17.280
If I don't eat more,

32:17.360 --> 32:19.560
how will I ever recoup
the brain cells I've lost?

32:21.480 --> 32:23.040
Order more. Eat up.

32:24.000 --> 32:26.560
Okay! Lady, take my order!

32:29.680 --> 32:32.040
It's a big restaurant. Servers are aloof.

32:34.080 --> 32:36.280
Eat up. Someone's picking up the tab.

32:43.240 --> 32:45.160
Does anyone have any suggestions?

32:45.240 --> 32:47.840
- If not, I'll just order.
- Go ahead.

32:50.720 --> 32:53.160
Two dozen oysters,
two dozen scallops,

32:54.440 --> 32:58.320
two dozen mussels,
and two plates of river snails.

33:00.440 --> 33:01.800
Does anyone want beer?

33:03.800 --> 33:06.400
Let's stick to red wine.
Beer doesn't go with seafood.

33:07.680 --> 33:09.360
Party pooper. Fine, wine it is.

33:09.440 --> 33:10.800
- Okay.
- Hurry up.

33:12.480 --> 33:15.320
Mr. Xiao, you're awesome.
Here, I'll drink to you.

33:15.400 --> 33:17.120
Thanks for the feast.

33:17.480 --> 33:19.440
Isn't tonight Hao Mei's treat?

33:21.880 --> 33:23.560
What? Why me?

33:25.080 --> 33:27.800
Before the meeting that day,
you were discussing

33:28.160 --> 33:29.880
where Hao Mei will treat us to seafood,

33:30.680 --> 33:33.640
on account of the two apartments.

33:37.320 --> 33:39.240
Right. I nearly forgot.

33:39.320 --> 33:41.840
Mei, a man's word is his word.

33:41.920 --> 33:43.280
This is your treat.

33:43.360 --> 33:45.680
- Right. A promise made is a promise kept.
- Yes!

33:45.960 --> 33:46.800
- Right?
- Yes.

33:46.880 --> 33:49.800
Help! Can I cancel the order?

33:50.240 --> 33:51.600
Mei, show some brass!

33:52.160 --> 33:54.320
Right. Don't be so stingy.

33:57.320 --> 33:59.920
- You're letting Nai off just like that?
- Right?

34:00.000 --> 34:02.440
Next weekend's road trip is on me.

34:05.800 --> 34:08.040
Mr. Xiao's so generous!

34:12.560 --> 34:14.480
Mei, what do you have to say now?

34:16.719 --> 34:18.440
Let's me check my bank card.

34:19.239 --> 34:22.440
Nai, you're the embodiment
of ruthlessness.

34:23.159 --> 34:26.800
You're too kind.
I'm only a dust storm, at most.

34:32.000 --> 34:33.679
Here. Have a crab.

34:35.000 --> 34:37.000
You're so vindictive.
I won't ever offend you.

34:37.080 --> 34:39.719
Too late. You just did.

34:50.840 --> 34:54.239
I didn't see this coming!
I'm paying for all this.

34:54.320 --> 34:57.520
This is all my money!
My blood and sweat!

34:57.600 --> 35:00.160
Your blood and sweat
aren't worth that much.

35:01.400 --> 35:02.440
Your blood and sweat.

35:04.240 --> 35:09.000
Mei, isn't it about time for you
to explain the real estate?

35:10.120 --> 35:11.200
- Right!
- That's right!

35:11.280 --> 35:13.200
My parents came to visit last month.

35:13.400 --> 35:15.000
I don't want to move back home.

35:15.080 --> 35:17.600
My parents bought the real estate
to urge me to get married.

35:19.120 --> 35:20.440
Why two apartments?

35:21.600 --> 35:22.560
Could it be...

35:24.440 --> 35:26.920
- You're getting two wives?
- Nai, why are you...

35:27.320 --> 35:30.000
Dust storms are unforgiving.

35:34.200 --> 35:35.120
Here you go.

35:37.240 --> 35:38.840
We don't even have a girl.

35:39.400 --> 35:41.320
He's marrying two girls.

35:41.600 --> 35:44.320
- Right?
- Two girls!

35:44.400 --> 35:46.160
Wait.

35:46.640 --> 35:48.080
I nearly forgot.

35:48.160 --> 35:51.040
I have an empty room in the apartment.

35:51.360 --> 35:53.240
Who wants to stay there? Rent-free!

35:53.440 --> 35:54.960
Me.

35:56.520 --> 35:58.720
But the room is very small.

35:58.920 --> 36:01.720
It can only fit one person, you...

36:02.400 --> 36:06.160
Bro, we lived together for four years.

36:06.440 --> 36:07.840
- Enough.
- You won't abandon me now?

36:07.920 --> 36:10.240
- He abandoned me!
- Your place is huge. Get lost!

36:10.320 --> 36:13.720
Mei and I have showered together.
What about you?

36:15.120 --> 36:18.280
Yugong, you'd better think it through.

36:18.360 --> 36:22.040
If you bring your girlfriend home,

36:22.320 --> 36:25.360
- Mei might steal her away.
- That's right!

36:25.440 --> 36:28.640
Then I'll take my girlfriend
and stay with Mei forever.

36:30.040 --> 36:32.680
Your feet stink so bad.
Mei couldn't handle it.

36:33.240 --> 36:34.720
No way! His feet stink even worse.

36:34.800 --> 36:38.080
- He doesn't wash his socks!
- Your feet stink, you grind your teeth...

36:38.160 --> 36:39.920
Enough.

36:40.320 --> 36:41.600
We're all buddies.

36:41.680 --> 36:43.880
I'd feel bad, no matter who lives there.

36:43.960 --> 36:45.760
You guys work it out.

36:46.000 --> 36:48.040
Just tell me the result, okay?

36:48.120 --> 36:49.080
That settles it.

37:01.920 --> 37:02.960
Come on, let's drink.

37:03.040 --> 37:04.200
- Let's drink!
- Drink!

37:04.280 --> 37:06.240
- Drink!
- Fill my glass.

37:06.320 --> 37:08.120
Why isn't Ashuang here?

37:09.040 --> 37:10.080
He quit.

37:11.480 --> 37:13.880
Did he really betray everyone?

37:14.920 --> 37:15.880
How did you know?

37:19.000 --> 37:20.400
I went to see Erxi,

37:20.640 --> 37:23.360
and saw Ashuang with a stranger.

37:23.440 --> 37:24.360
Today,

37:24.440 --> 37:26.760
I went with Erxi,
to pick up her intern pay.

37:26.840 --> 37:29.680
I found out he's in charge of
Zhenyi's game development.

37:30.520 --> 37:33.360
I knew something was wrong,
so I tried to call you,

37:33.440 --> 37:34.720
but your phone was turned off.

37:34.800 --> 37:37.200
- Don't listen to him. Let's drink.
- Okay!

37:37.280 --> 37:39.440
We were at the demo.
I had to turn it off.

37:40.160 --> 37:41.720
Mei has real estate!

37:43.080 --> 37:45.760
Why did Ashuang do something like that?

37:46.000 --> 37:48.480
Here's to you.

37:48.560 --> 37:50.120
Let's drink a toast.

38:05.000 --> 38:07.720
Mr. Xiao, I need to talk to you.

38:10.960 --> 38:12.200
I want to know why.

38:14.600 --> 38:17.160
You already know, Boss?

38:21.560 --> 38:25.600
A childhood friend of mine
developed a little game,

38:26.440 --> 38:31.960
but his girlfriend sold it to Zhenyi
behind his back.

38:33.440 --> 38:35.080
In a fit of rage,

38:35.160 --> 38:37.880
my friend still launched the game.

38:38.960 --> 38:43.000
Zhenyi then sued him
for stealing trade secrets.

38:45.600 --> 38:47.200
Zhenyi came to me for this.

38:49.200 --> 38:51.120
This friend means a lot to me,

38:51.200 --> 38:53.080
so I had to betray Zhiyi.

38:54.200 --> 38:56.440
But I only told them our progress.

38:56.520 --> 38:58.760
I never revealed anything else, so you...

39:07.520 --> 39:10.400
Sorry, Boss.

39:15.040 --> 39:17.360
Cheers.

39:18.000 --> 39:19.480
I see.

39:20.240 --> 39:22.600
Do Yugong and the others know?

39:25.920 --> 39:27.280
They don't need to know.

39:36.240 --> 39:37.560
You had it tough, Head of Household.

39:37.640 --> 39:39.120
Oyster?

39:39.200 --> 39:40.160
What?

39:40.640 --> 39:44.760
Nothing. Hurry and grow up,
Mrs. Head of Household.

39:45.960 --> 39:48.440
Have you all had enough to eat and drink?
Let's go sing!

39:48.520 --> 39:50.800
- Come on.
- Let's go sing.

39:51.680 --> 39:53.800
K.O., come on! Let's sing!

39:55.000 --> 39:56.560
Sure, let's sing.

39:56.640 --> 39:58.400
I'll sing first.

39:58.480 --> 40:00.280
- Who'll go first?
- Me!

40:00.360 --> 40:02.080
- He'll go.
- Come, I'll take you home.

40:02.640 --> 40:05.120
- What about--
- It's fine. I called them cabs.

40:05.200 --> 40:07.040
- Okay.
- Let's go pay.

40:08.280 --> 40:10.440
Isn't Mr. Girly paying for this?

40:10.520 --> 40:13.440
I was just kidding.
He'll be pleasantly surprised.

40:13.520 --> 40:15.000
- Okay, let's go.
- Yu, drink up!

40:16.920 --> 40:18.720
Have fun, guys. We're taking off.

40:18.800 --> 40:20.640
- Leaving?
- Are you leaving?

40:22.040 --> 40:22.880
Already?

40:22.960 --> 40:25.280
Bye, Boss.

40:26.280 --> 40:28.080
- Let's get the party started!
- Come on!

40:28.160 --> 40:30.800
Let's get the party started!

41:25.000 --> 41:27.800
Half past three in the afternoon? So late.

41:29.120 --> 41:30.440
Who is it?

41:31.800 --> 41:32.800
Coming!

41:34.960 --> 41:37.280
Coming.

41:42.200 --> 41:43.040
Who is it?

41:45.840 --> 41:48.560
K.O.? What are you doing here?

41:51.160 --> 41:52.280
Working the the back channels.

44:21.880 --> 44:24.320
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
